Package com.att.android.arodatacollector.main

Contains interfaces, classes and enumerations for handling the main services of the ARO Data Collector.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AROCollectorCustomDialog.DialogKeyListner
    Exposes a method for listening to Key events from custom ARO Data Collector dialogs.
    AROCollectorCustomDialog.ReadyListener
    Exposes a method for listening to responses from AROCollectorCustomDialog.Dialog_CallBack_Error dialogs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AROCollectorCustomDialog
    Represents a custom dialog in the ARO Data Collector which is used for confirmation messages and errors.
    AROCollectorService
    Contains methods for managing the tcpdump and video capture processes while recording a trace during the application life-cycle.
    AROCollectorTaskManagerDetailProcess
    Represents the process details of the rows in the ARO Data Collector task killer.
    AROCollectorTaskManagerListAdapters
    Represents a custom list adapter for the ARO Data Collector task killer which is used to store list view data.
    AROCollectorTaskManagerListAdapters.ProcessListAdapter
    Represents a custom list adapter for the ARO Data Collector task killer that contains a list of processes.
    AROCollectorTaskManagerPackagesInfo
    Represents a package of application information for the ARO Data Collector task killer.
    AROCollectorTaskManagerProcessInfo
    Represents task killer process information for the ARO Data Collector.
    AROCollectorTaskManagerProcessInfo.PsRow
    Represents one row of PS (native shell command) data for the ARO Data Collector task killer.
    AROCollectorTraceService
    An ARO Data Collector service class that captures trace data from device peripherals traces (like Wifi and GPS) during data collection.
    ARODataCollector
    Represents the ARO Data Collector application.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AROCollectorCustomDialog.Dialog_CallBack_Error
    The Dialog_CallBack_Error enumeration specifies constant values that describe the types of callback methods associated with error message dialogs.
    AROCollectorCustomDialog.Dialog_Type
    The Dialog_Type enumeration specifies constant values that describe the types of custom dialogs used in the ARO Data Collector.

Package com.att.android.arodatacollector.main Description

Contains interfaces, classes and enumerations for handling the main services of the ARO Data Collector.

Contains interfaces that provide methods for reading and responding to user input, classes for handling data in the ARO Data Collector, and enumerations that describe custom dialog types.
